    <section class="about-us">
<h2>About Us</h2>

<img src="image9.jpg" alt="founders">

      <p>At Capricho's, we're more than just a bakery; we're a family dedicated to creating delicious and heartwarming treats. Our journey began with Linda and Tania, who have always held a deep passion for baking. Growing up, their [insert missing memory about baking]. This love for baking blossomed into a dream of sharing their creations with the world.</p>

      <p>In 2014, Linda along with Tania, decided to turn their dream into reality. We opened the doors of Capricho's, a haven for those seeking fresh-baked goodness and a taste of home.</p>

      <p>Our commitment to quality is unwavering. We use only the finest ingredients, from locally sourced flour and butter to seasonal fruits and decadent chocolates. We believe that fresh, high-quality ingredients are the foundation for truly exceptional baked goods.</p>

      <p>But Capricho's is more than just ingredients. It's about the love and care poured into every pastry, cake, and loaf. Our team of passionate bakers, each with their own unique skills and creativity, are the heart of our bakery. They take pride in crafting each treat with meticulous attention to detail, ensuring every bite is a delightful experience.</p>

      <p>We believe that baked goods have the power to bring people together. Whether it's a morning croissant enjoyed with a cup of coffee, a birthday cake shared with loved ones, or a slice of pie that evokes nostalgic memories, we hope our creations become a part of your special moments.</p>

      <p>At Capricho's, we're not just baking treats; we're baking happiness. We invite you to visit us, experience the warmth of our bakery, and savor the taste of our passion in every bite.</p>
    </section>
     
